https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9KgAArJuSDM&list=PLk1kxccoEnNEtwGZW-3KAcAlhI_Guwh8x&index=25

🍉️1. updating the arrays.
  --> update sal_emp set pay='{25000,25000,25000,25000}' where name='sanjay';

🍉️2.Updating the individual value.
  --> update sal_emp set pay[2]=30000 where name='sanjay';

🍉️3.slicing update.
  --> update sal_emp set pay[1:2]='{20000,30000}' where name='vikas';

🍉️4.Appending array in every row.
  --> update sal_emp set pay=array_append(pay,55000);


🍉️5.Concatinating the multiple values into array.
  --> update sal_emp set pay=array_cat(pay,ARRAY[11000,12000]);

🍉️6.removing the array elements.
  --> update sal_emp set pay=array_remove(pay,25000);
